OL,3,CSisters accidentally drowned while
OL,4,Cpaddling fully clothed, inquest hears
OL,6,FTwo sisters accidentally drowned after
OL,7,Fthey paddled fully clothed at a beauty
OL,8,Fspot in Eryri National Park
OL,9,F(Snowdonia), an inquest has heard.
OL,11,FMarried mother-of-two Hajra Zahid, 29,
OL,12,Fand her sister Haleema, 25, were
OL,13,Fpulled from pools on the Watkin Path
OL,14,Fwhich leads to the summit of Yr
OL,15,FWyddfa, or Snowdon, in north Wales.
OL,17,FBoth visited the picturesque wild
OL,18,Fswimming site and its waterfall ` made
OL,19,Fpopular by social media ` on the early
OL,20,Fevening of June 11, 2025, with three
OL,21,Fmale friends.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
