CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772809879
OL,3,CSisters accidentally drowned while
OL,4,Cpaddling fully clothed, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe group of five, who were all
OL,7,Fstudents at the University of Chester,
OL,8,Fsplit up for privacy and religious
OL,9,Freasons as the sisters, who could not
OL,10,Fswim, headed for a pool upstream on
OL,11,Fthe Afon Cwm Llan river.
OL,13,FThe males later called out for the
OL,14,Fsisters, from Maltby, Rotherham, but
OL,15,Fgot no reply to their shouts and when
OL,16,Fthey reached the pools they noticed
OL,17,Ftheir shoes and personal belongings at
OL,18,Fthe side.
OL,20,FThey later discovered Hajra floating
OL,21,Fface down in her red dress.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
