PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772809879
OL,3,CSisters accidentally drowned while
OL,4,Cpaddling fully clothed, inquest hears
OL,6,FCaernarfon Coroner's Court was told
OL,7,Fthey managed to pull an unconscious
OL,8,FHajra onto the river bank but they
OL,9,Fwere unable to find Haleema.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called and two
OL,12,Fmembers of Llanberis Mountain Rescue
OL,13,FTeam later retrieved Haleema, who was
OL,14,Fwearing blue jeans and a black shirt,
OL,15,Ffrom deep water near the waterfall.
OL,17,FShortly after, both women were
OL,18,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
