OL,3,CSisters accidentally drowned while
OL,4,Cpaddling fully clothed, inquest hears
OL,6,FDetective Constable Gutun Lake, from
OL,7,FNorth Wales Police, told the inquests
OL,8,Fthat the group of five including
OL,9,FLuqman Zeb, Jawad Iqbal and Hassan
OL,10,FKhan, all from Liverpool, had earlier
OL,11,Fvisited Llandudno.
OL,13,FThey then headed to Eryri National
OL,14,FPark and parked up before a 40-minute
OL,15,Fwalk to the stream.
OL,17,FHe said it was a "very hot day" with
OL,18,Ftemperatures exceeding 30C and that
OL,19,Fthe pools were, in comparison, said to
OL,20,Fbe "extremely cold".
