OL,3,CSisters accidentally drowned while
OL,4,Cpaddling fully clothed, inquest hears
OL,6,FAssistant Coroner for North West
OL,7,FWales, Sarah Riley, said she found
OL,8,Fthat the sisters had intended to
OL,9,Fpaddle in the water.
OL,11,FShe said: "Having considered the
OL,12,Fevidence that neither could swim and
OL,13,Fthat they were fully clothed I am
OL,14,Fsatisfied that neither sister went to
OL,15,Fswim or enter parts of the pool that
OL,16,Fwould put them out of their depths in
OL,17,Fthe water."
OL,26,@sD@KOUyD@KO]
