OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772809879
OL,3,CSisters accidentally drowned while
OL,4,Cpaddling fully clothed, inquest hears
OL,6,FShe said one possibility was that one
OL,7,For both had fallen from an
OL,8,F"exceptionally slippy" slab of rock at
OL,9,Fthe edge of the pools.
OL,11,FThe inquest heard that the mountain
OL,12,Fteam rescuers who entered the water
OL,13,Fhad both slipped on the same rock.
OL,15,FConcluding their deaths were
OL,16,Faccidental, she said the sisters had
OL,17,Fboth drowned after they were unable to
OL,18,Fswim to safety.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@VO]
