OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772809879
OL,3,CSisters accidentally drowned while
OL,4,Cpaddling fully clothed, inquest hears
OL,6,FShe said: "I extend my sincere
OL,7,Fcondolences to their friends and
OL,8,Ffamily. This is an extremely tragic
OL,9,Fcase and my thoughts remain with them."
OL,11,FMs Riley also "urged caution" to the
OL,12,Fpublic about the dangers of entering
OL,13,Fsuch pools.
OL,15,FThe sisters, from Rawalpindi,
OL,16,FPakistan, came to the UK in January
OL,17,F2025 to study a Master's degree in
OL,18,Finternational business.
