OL,3,CSisters accidentally drowned while
OL,4,Cpaddling fully clothed, inquest hears
OL,6,FIn a statement read out at the
OL,7,Finquests, Hajra's husband Hessham
OL,8,FMinhas said she "always placed herself
OL,9,Fat the centre of family life".
OL,11,FHe said: "She was a determined,
OL,12,Fambitious woman who believed in the
OL,13,Fpower of education and personal
OL,14,Fgrowth, with a dream of building a
OL,15,Fbetter future for herself and her
OL,16,Ffamily. Her memory lives on in the
OL,17,Flives she touched and the family she
OL,18,Fleft behind."
OL,26,@pD@QOUqD@]O]sD@JOUzD@MO]
