OL,3,CSisters accidentally drowned while
OL,4,Cpaddling fully clothed, inquest hears
OL,6,FAnother statement from Raja Azem, a
OL,7,Ffriend of Haleema, said: "Haleema will
OL,8,Fremain in our hearts and prayers as a
OL,9,Floving, daughter, sister and auntie."
